1
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:38,039
Recently, Chinese police and the Royal Thai Police

2
00:01:38,039 --> 00:01:39,200
carried out transnational police cooperation.

3
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,080
They successfully cracked a major

4
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:41,640
transnational artifact smuggling case.

5
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,840
They destroyed a criminal group long active

6
00:01:42,840 --> 00:01:44,080
in artifact smuggling on the China-Thailand border.

7
00:01:44,080 --> 00:01:46,120
The head of the Royal Thai Police's

8
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,080
Antiquities Crime Investigation Bureau stated

9
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:48,240
that this cooperation is an important achievement

10
00:01:48,240 --> 00:01:50,039
in protecting cultural heritage for both countries.

11
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:52,039
Relevant Chinese officials emphasized

12
00:01:52,039 --> 00:01:54,400
that artifact smuggling severely damages human cultural heritage.

13
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:56,960
They will fully cut off the transnational smuggling chain.

14
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:58,280
The head of the syndicate,

15
00:01:58,280 --> 00:02:00,640
a suspect nicknamed Black Snake, is currently at large.

16
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,920
Interpol has issued

17
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,480
a Red Notice for him.

18
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:05,800
Stop.

19
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:37,800
Stop.

20
00:02:58,480 --> 00:02:59,210
Black Snake.

21
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,680
Or should I call you Brother?

22
00:03:04,040 --> 00:03:06,600
If you're here to mock me,

23
00:03:06,720 --> 00:03:08,640
I'm going to disappoint you.

24
00:03:09,920 --> 00:03:11,160
As long as you don't have

25
00:03:11,160 --> 00:03:12,440
the Tears of Buluotuo,

26
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,660
you haven't won

27
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,600
a single day.

28
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,300
You guessed wrong.

29
00:03:19,079 --> 00:03:20,560
I'm here to admit defeat.

30
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:22,920
Give up?

31
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,840
Don't be ridiculous.

32
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,440
It's true.

33
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:27,320
From the very beginning,

34
00:03:27,320 --> 00:03:28,520
our choice was wrong.

35
00:03:28,600 --> 00:03:29,600
Buluotuo's Tears

36
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,360
have long been empty.

37
00:03:32,400 --> 00:03:34,060
You're bluffing, aren't you?

38
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:36,690
Do you remember?

39
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,440
Eternal youth,

40
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:42,170
bringing the dead back to life.

41
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:43,960
Eternal youth

42
00:03:46,079 --> 00:03:47,280
is just a legend.

43
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:58,800
If that's the case,

44
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:02,040
you'll never beat me.

45
00:04:03,640 --> 00:04:05,360
I will never lose to you.

46
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,720
Since we've both lost,

47
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,760
let's let go of our obsessions.

48
00:04:18,760 --> 00:04:20,089
Whether we let go or not,

49
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:23,610
it doesn't matter anymore.

50
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:30,120
There's no turning back.

51
00:04:38,159 --> 00:04:39,880
Look at me one last time.

52
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:46,200
You'll always be in my heart, Brother.

53
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:41,440
I never expected

54
00:05:42,080 --> 00:05:43,159
that Buluotuo's Tears,

55
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:44,600
which we've been searching for so long,

56
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,600
actually fell into the Meinan River

57
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,200
a thousand years ago.

58
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,600
I just wonder if the river

59
00:05:54,240 --> 00:05:57,170
still has the miraculous power to cure all diseases.

60
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,840
Liu Yu.

61
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,980
I haven't released my river lantern yet.

62
00:06:08,040 --> 00:06:08,440
You...

63
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:10,210
aren't another AI, are you?

64
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:14,640
I had a very long dream.

65
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:17,020
There was a boy in my dream.

66
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,560
For the sake of a promise,

67
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,730
he almost stayed in another world.

68
00:06:28,120 --> 00:06:29,650
Let's release it together.

69
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:01,280
Bulotuo's Tears

70
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:04,080
have long since merged into the Chao Phraya River.

71
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,260
China and Thailand

72
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,680
have shared the same river for centuries.

73
00:07:07,680 --> 00:07:09,000
That is a long-standing bond.
